&lt;li&gt;Review &amp;amp; reconcile new contracts &amp;amp; assess related contracts/projects including understanding contract components of milestones/tasks and intercompany components &amp;amp; ensuring accuracy of project set up.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
