&lt;li&gt;Set up new clients in accounting systems and files including adding and mapping employees to new billable&amp;nbsp;rates, and&amp;nbsp;review of MSA&#39;s for rebates and discounts.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Review intercompany revenue/cost transactions &amp;amp;&amp;nbsp;updating&amp;nbsp;shared financial trackers.&lt;/li&gt;
