&lt;li&gt;3–5 years of experience with SQL Server, data integration, ETL development, and data validation techniques.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong command of data storytelling and the ability to explain complex logic to diverse audiences.&lt;/li&gt;
